  "title": "Retail Supervisor (Retail, Islandwide)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Manage all aspects of a designated product category, including inventory control, pricing accuracy, product presentation, and sales performance analysis.</li>\n  <li>Create and implement initiatives to boost sales growth while aligning category goals with the overall objectives of the store.</li>\n  <li>Provide training, coaching, and support to retail staff to enhance product knowledge, customer service, and operational efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with merchandising teams and suppliers to address promotional activities and resolve issues, ensuring a positive customer shopping experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE O Level and above</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of <strong>supervisory</strong> experience in <strong>retail sales.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of inventory management, pricing strategies, and visual merchandising.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in <strong>MS Word</strong> to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
